{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132970/extras/Hoverboard_steam.gif?t=1726491544\" /><br><br>Time To Stop Time is a first-person superhero action. You\u2019re given the power to control time and a huge responsibility to save every innocent person from the imminent danger. There is a limited time to analyse the situation and navigate through a storm of falling debris, bullets and explosions.<br><br>Choose your own solution for each situation and find the most creative way to resolve an imminent crisis!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time-frozen physics</h2>Change the trajectory of moving bullets to send them back. Throw and move different objects to create a path or improvised weapons.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Extreme surfing </h2>Jump on a rocket or a tank shell, turning it into an explosive hoverboard.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">40+ Time Sandbox Levels</h2>From simple bar brawls to saving the President \u2014 each level is unique and it\u2019s up to you how to solve its puzzles.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tactical kicking</h2>Accelerate objects or your enemies with a good kick.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Throw knives</h2>Throw multiple knives at enemies.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time skip</h2>Move objects forward in time, send bullets straight to enemy faces!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rally The Troops","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1132970/42ce345381715bc91cf5612f849619aac5dd3683.jpg"},{"name":"The Apocalypse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1132970/ba98fcdf30e2725bcd60a985205796e64c9e3e78.jpg"},{"name":"Classified","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1132970/e30de2c783a0b84b2d59afe6ff227d08fca2df1a.jpg"},{"name":"Nazi Scheme","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommu